<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>بِسْمِ اللَّهِ الرَّحْمنِ الرَّحِيمِ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>[سورة الإخلاص <span class="c2">(١١٢)</span> : الآيات ١ الى ٤]<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>بِسْمِ اللَّهِ الرَّحْمنِ الرَّحِيمِ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>قُلْ هُوَ اللَّهُ أَحَدٌ <span class="c2">(١)</span> اللَّهُ الصَّمَدُ <span class="c2">(٢)</span> لَمْ يَلِدْ وَلَمْ يُولَدْ <span class="c2">(٣)</span> وَلَمْ يَكُنْ لَهُ كُفُواً أَحَدٌ <span class="c2">(٤)</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>١-<span class="c5"> قُلْ هُوَ اللَّهُ أَحَدٌ:</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>أَحَدٌ لا سواه ولا شريك له.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>٢-<span class="c5"> اللَّهُ الصَّمَدُ:</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>الصَّمَدُ المقصود وحده فى الحوائج.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>٣-<span class="c5"> لَمْ يَلِدْ وَلَمْ يُولَدْ:</span><a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>لَمْ يَلِدْ لم يتخذ ولدا.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>وَلَمْ يُولَدْ من أب أو أم.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>٤-<span class="c5"> وَلَمْ يَكُنْ لَهُ كُفُواً أَحَدٌ:</span><a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>كُفُواً شبيها أو نظيرا، ليس كمثله شىء.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>